msgid "Scenario IX: Return to Turn Back Time"
msgstr "冒险IX：重返时间倒流"

msgid "Set the following cards aside, out of play: The Harbinger of Valusia enemy, the 3 Pit Viper cards from the <i>Serpents</i> encounter set, and the Chamber of Time location."
msgstr "将下列卡牌放在一边，位于场外：瓦卢西亚的预示者敌人卡、 从<i>蛇族</i>遭遇组中找出的3张蝮蛇卡牌、时间石室地点卡。"
